Class TypedHashMap<K,V>

Object

          TypedHashMap<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - Key type (for compile-time)
V - Value type (for compile-time)
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Map<K,V>
public class TypedHashMap<K,V>
extends HashMap<K,V>

This class created to make possible getting Key and Value types in runtime environment. Actually it's just usual HashMap with ability of getting Key and Value types in runtime. Note: You should set Key and Value types as constructor parameters
